274
0:17:25,411 --> 0:17:27,88
NARRATOR:
Magic and science


275
0:17:27,88 --> 0:17:30,783
have been intertwined
throughout human history,


276
0:17:30,783 --> 0:17:33,919
and the Ulfberht merged
