319
0:20:6,238 --> 0:20:8,907
The theory is that this is
how they did it


320
0:20:8,907 --> 0:20:15,447
a thousand years ago.


321
0:20:15,447 --> 0:20:18,684
Charcoal will burn
hot enough to melt steel.


322
0:20:18,684 --> 0:20:24,289
