331
0:20:55,354 --> 0:21:2,427
And then we have our starting
material for the Ulfberht.


332
0:21:2,427 --> 0:21:33,992
Last brick.


333
0:21:33,992 --> 0:21:37,429
NARRATOR:
Closed at the top and vented from the side,


334
0:21:37,429 --> 0:21:40,32
